data.description: The Indian & Tex Mex cuisine joins hand to arrive on your platter at your favorite all day dining joint, – the newly furbished & revamped multi cuisine restaurant in Jamshedpur “CINNAMON”. As you step into the place a rich and mystic aura welcomes you, the interiors designed to match the color of the rugged spice which forms an inevitable ingredient in the global kitchen. From the border regions of Texas and Mexico to the ancient kitchens of India, dining at CINNAMON is sure to make you feel that food has no boundaries, taste buds do not restrict them to any region. You walk away with a sheer dining pleasure worth a remembrance… Breakfast Buffet: 6:00am to 10:00am Lunch Buffet: 12:00pm to 11:00pm Special Sunday Brunch: 11:30pm to 03:30pm
